01:56:14,327 --> 01:56:17,285
Back to your very first words?

1071
01:56:18,607 --> 01:56:21,440
"30 minutes", you said.

1072
01:56:25,447 --> 01:56:31,079
"Give me 30 minutes, and you will
never want to leave me again."

