01:59:28,807 --> 01:59:31,765
Two days later he was gone.

1079
01:59:32,207 --> 01:59:35,085
I don't know if he will come back.

1080
01:59:35,207 --> 01:59:38,649
I am surprised that I am
not suffering more.

1081
01:59:38,650 --> 01:59:39,644
