1083
01:59:44,207 --> 01:59:47,193
I need to mop up the
floor of the apartment

1084
01:59:47,194 --> 01:59:50,043
and I am desperately
looking for some flowers.

1085
01:59:50,167 --> 01:59:53,000
Yesterday I found some lilac.

1086
01:59:54,207 --> 01:59:57,040
I wonder if Gerd still thinks about me.

1087
01:59:57,247 --> 01:59:59,203
Who knows?

1088
01:59:59,367 --> 02:00:01,692
Maybe our hearts have
a say in this, too,

1089
02:00:01,893 --> 02:00:05,197
and we'll see each other again,
some day.

